{"tid":2049960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國ban鳩支那登記民航機飛去美國，唔知而家匯豐同渣打驚唔驚","createTime":"2020-06-03T22:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T23:23:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a19c58017961bbcaa07dc0d2bb8c6a8fc91c6c17","tid":2049960,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T22:44:36.000Z","msg":"渣打銀行發言人表示，相信「港區國安法」有助香港長遠穩定，希望最終立法條文更加清晰，令香港得以保持經濟及社會穩定。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，滙豐銀行副主席兼行政總裁、香港總商會主席王冬勝接受《新華社》訪問時說，香港商界十分關心「港區國安法」，他接觸很多商會同仁，絕大多數認為可以確保香港繼續成為國際金融中心，而作為一個國際城市，穩定最為重要，穩定是一切發展的基礎和前提。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530045-20200604.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530045-20200604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=b793da0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530045-20200604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ba889a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530045-20200604.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a7a0f7655d26170fdec16d6a2a96957e560bb1f7","tid":2049960,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T22:46:58.000Z","msg":"其實呢兩間行係美國都冇乜實務"},{"pid":"1d925e9ff87260fe1267955890b8c81a21d8b806","tid":2049960,"uid":291487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7a0f7655d26170fdec16d6a2a96957e560bb1f7","tid":2049960,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T22:46:58.000Z","msg":"其實呢兩間行係美國都冇乜實務"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T22:52:19.000Z","msg":"但係要美金？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646f732752d1754766da951d033527efbcb60071","tid":2049960,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7a0f7655d26170fdec16d6a2a96957e560bb1f7","tid":2049960,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci